data.description: Updated Eagle Ridge Rancher. Move-In Ready, All New Carpet throughout, New Landscaping & Professionally Cleaned, must see this 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom Rancher with main level laundry! Enjoy comfort amenities; gas forced air heat & AC. Landscaped, in-ground sprinklers, fenced backyard, large deck. Inviting front porch welcomes to the great room living room w/cathedral ceiling & open floor plan. Light’n bright kitchen offers all appliances & pantry. Large primary ensuite w/bathroom, shower, dual vanity sinks & large wardrobe closet. 2 & 3rd bedrooms, full bathroom, laundry/utility room & 2 car garage. Finished basement offers large den, 4th bedroom, full bathroom, storage room & bonus rec room.  Close-in Latah shopping center, Yokes groceries, Chaps Bakery. Quick commute routes to I-195 & I-90, downtown Spokane & Cheney, Fairchild Airforce Base, West Plains, Amazon Airway Heights & Spokane Valley to Coeur d’Alene (40 mins). See Video tour, You Will Love This Home!
